column1: Comparison of user-controlled data of different kinds
column2: Comparing different kinds of HTTP request data may be a symptom of an insufficient security check.
column4: This comparison of [["req.cookies"|"relative:///VulnFinder-CodeQL-main/src/javascript-cwe/CWE-807/examples/bypass.js:6:9:6:19"]] and [["req.params.userId"|"relative:///VulnFinder-CodeQL-main/src/javascript-cwe/CWE-807/examples/bypass.js:6:40:6:56"]] is a potential security risk since it is controlled by the user.
